" * `B` &nbsp;&nbsp; _druhá testovaná položka (pre binárne testy)_\n"
" * `L` &nbsp;&nbsp; _aktuálne testovaná vrstva_\n"
"\n"
"<br>\n"
"\n"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_rules_help_4severity_names.h:2
